{"tid":422362,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"KFC隻黑絲雞真係好撚難食","createTime":"2017-10-03T03:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T05:35:06.000Z","uid":74981,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3fc5012b2420486d039b73915cbabc41735498e","tid":422362,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e956111ec5b3526c993ab9c73a68f8584f0bcab8","tid":422362,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:58:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c62b1ba177de5a795906897ca111fc09e2dcf51f","tid":422362,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:58:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86f8ea40261f2b059cc0ec7e6822e798778e5d4e","tid":422362,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bf61c8c024f15be18627d4516f022eebf93e721","tid":422362,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:59:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da00455a63d9aebbeb728705fc73f2592519b455","tid":422362,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"肥c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf232e6df3c41935c9b7dbfbc04c4b45d76409cc","tid":422362,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"等本癲狗介紹下肥絲到底係何方神聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話到明肥絲, 緊係肥閪一條啦. 咁到底佢有幾撚肥? 不如睇下佢既自我介紹啦:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>原來男人老狗得果158CM高, 168磅!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/wg5s0sjbb/Truth_Weight.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2Fwg5s0sjbb%2FTruth_Weight.png&h=4237dead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得佢成日咁憎本癲狗啦, 因為本癲狗高條肥閪一截, 又冇條肥閪咁撚肥, 咁佢咪妒忌我承機攻擊我囉. 誰不知天網恢恢, 咁都俾我搵到條肥閪既自爆POST, 咁佢自己攞黎柒, 我都幫佢唔撚到啦<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然佢唔敢POST自己身型既相, 就等本癲狗幫佢一把啦, 男人身高158CM, 168磅既身型大慨係咁:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/fwrlxvnrv/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Ffwrlxvnrv%2Fimage.jpg&h=1787cf3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲原來係肥佬扮肥婆!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家唔知一定以為肥絲係女人啦, NO NO NO, 其實佢係男人黎, 睇下, 佢又自爆啦:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/i8z8gk3xt/Screenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fi8z8gk3xt%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png&h=6a188dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人老狗幻想自己係女人都算啦, 但竟然幻想自已係肥矮臭柒毒既肥婆, 誤導各位, 真係又核突, 又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過, 補充一點, 佢肥矮臭柒毒係事實, 不過係肥矮臭柒毒既麻甩佬, 並唔係肥婆囉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲自爆係畜牲?</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n原來肥絲除左肥矮臭柒毒之外, 原來仲好撚似猩猩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 各位睇下:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/4uvmleq7p/Screenshot_2017-05-27-10-13-54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2F4uvmleq7p%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-10-13-54.png&h=0463833c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲年齡之謎&hellip;</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實肥絲咁撚ON9, 大家估下佢幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哩層本癲狗都無法判斷, 請各位巴打分析下:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n84日前, 牠27歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/472926oth/27_84.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2F472926oth%2F27_84.png&h=71a99850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n110日前, 牠30歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/n706uevsl/30_110.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2Fn706uevsl%2F30_110.png&h=4c570172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n154日前, 牠24歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/gf9qghnsp/24_154.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fgf9qghnsp%2F24_154.png&h=0a9f11af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n170日前, 牠31歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/n1ezatkgh/31_170.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fn1ezatkgh%2F31_170.png&h=92e0b647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n175日前, 牠25歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/9j52syre7/25_175.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F9j52syre7%2F25_175.png&h=7727adf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n179日前, 牠27歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.postimg.org/dulrpdl7x/27_179.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.postimg.org%2Fdulrpdl7x%2F27_179.png&h=0127f621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n180日前, 牠30歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s29.postimg.org/d7irbcnc7/30_180.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs29.postimg.org%2Fd7irbcnc7%2F30_180.png&h=0a4a9f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥絲, 好心你寫野MAKE SENSE D 啦, 成日學人講邏輯, 話人唔撚夠你講, 咁宜家你又解唔解釋到哩個呀傻閪? 你都係匿番入你老母個閪扮睇唔到算啦, 無謂衝出黎柒啦<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>癲狗感想:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n肥絲, 其實你做埋咁多野，大費周章，起哂我底，圖文並茂，本癲狗真係好開心架，因為好少可真係有d狗俾我撚到發哂火，非係要整鳩我不可，我的目的已經達到了<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" />雖然你咁有心機整咁大篇垃圾批鬥文出黎，但來來去去都係得果幾條基佬撐你，全世界都當你傻閪，唔想理你，咁你都唔洗遷怒於我架? 你估你又好好咩? 男人老狗幻想自己係女都算，但幻想自己係d狗都唔屌既油脂肥婆，你係唔係老母中撚在幅射生到你心理變態呀? 真係人唔笑，狗都吠呀<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知你老母生到你又肥又基又弱智，現實廢鳩一條，只能做鍵盤戰士，你好憎佢，想佢日日俾人屌，但你都唔洗借本癲狗過橋架? 你老母做雞，我已經盡量幫襯多d，屌到佢閪皮都化埋，你唔洗再引其他人屌佢啦，做人唔好咁撚不孝先得架<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係因為你自小就因為肥矮臭柒毒所以俾人排斥, 冇朋友, 冇人注意, 所以一上網就要做鍵盤戰士, 引人注意, 認為嘈交贏左就係&quot;打贏仗&quot;, 將自己開既post叫做&quot;戰場&quot;. 可惜, 你對住本癲狗就從來都未贏過一仗, 連自己自以為擅長既地方都俾人打敗, 唔怪得你咁憎我啦. <img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15fcc73f808dfb2ec85eb49f6593606d173559cd","tid":422362,"uid":1085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a8082a69f0617c8fd76fc8f6cef0b39508f268f","tid":422362,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"肥閪你篇垃圾冇人睇架啦, 睇我哩篇好過啦<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左大家更了解位連登隻畜牲既所作所為, 本癲狗帶大家進行深入探討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n網名：肥絲大隻<br />\n編號：21423<br />\n身高：158厘米<br />\n體重：168磅<br />\n居住：估計應該係狗籠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特徵：矮、肥、柒、毒、臭<br />\n嗜好：幻想自己係律師, 雄辯淊淊, 可惜除左佢班狗同伴以外, 無人想理佢, 連ADMIN都當鳩佢傻仔無視佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1. 肥閪黑歷史, 得罪人多, 犯眾憎</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>肥絲大隻糾正ABC張曦雯英文</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/110910/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/110910/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n其實肥絲柒都唔係第一日架啦, 不過估唔到佢真係柒到以為自己有料Challenge人地張曦雯d英文, 人地話哂完成小學四年級後跟屋企人移民至美國芝加哥咁耐, 英文會差得過條肥閪? 肥閪小學四年班果陣做緊咩呀? 應該仲係度on99比同學排斥杯葛緊咋<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>肥絲大隻帶頭block人</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/162651/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/162651/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n柒頭肥絲又唔知做咩on9得罪人, 連續比38頁既巴打絲打毫不留情地block<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/a8mntgqbf/Block.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fa8mntgqbf%2FBlock.jpg&h=897724c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢柒既程度真係史無前例, 哩點佢可以贏到本癲狗<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2. 就因為肥閪人氣差, 於是就想藉著打擊本癲狗上位, 可惜各位巴打絲打眼晴係雪亮既, 大部份都支持本癲狗, 除左少數畜牲會企係佢果邊之外</ins></strong><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/ysubhparn/Screenshot_2017-05-29-21-32-28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fysubhparn%2FScreenshot_2017-05-29-21-32-28.png&h=5502e14e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係佢對本癲狗作出第一輪攻擊前, 已經有好多巴打支持本癲狗同屌鳩條肥閪:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/qnp5kvax7/Before_1st_attack.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Fqnp5kvax7%2FBefore_1st_attack.jpg&h=1bfadd26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來肥絲被本癲狗撚到潛哂水, 不過佢又唔服, 於是作出零星反抗:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/f916lhd5n/Screenshot_2017-05-29-21-23-19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Ff916lhd5n%2FScreenshot_2017-05-29-21-23-19.png&h=43f474d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜各位都無視佢整左三日三夜既成果, 繼續支持本癲狗同屌鳩條肥閪:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s17.postimg.org/xckosaaz3/After_1st_Attack.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs17.postimg.org%2Fxckosaaz3%2FAfter_1st_Attack.jpg&h=8043c150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是肥絲又被我撚到忍唔住, 發表第二輪零星攻勢, 大慨就係補充左幾頁廢話之類的...<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/7vw9ovpxn/Screenshot_2017-05-29-21-26-35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2F7vw9ovpxn%2FScreenshot_2017-05-29-21-26-35.png&h=08511494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜各位都繼續無視佢 (除左幾件微不足道既蛋散), 繼續支持本癲狗同屌鳩條肥閪:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/6bqhp0qb3/After_2nd_attack.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F6bqhp0qb3%2FAfter_2nd_attack.jpg&h=3c1d117a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實肥絲你同你班狗契仔唔好再作無謂既反抗啦, 你咁做同想用流星錘打架戰機落黎有咩分別呢? 以下係肥絲既抗強而無力既反抗圖<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/gzt7y84vl/0_GAC6_S0_ATJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fgzt7y84vl%2F0_GAC6_S0_ATJ.gif&h=a4d0a651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3. 肥絲無力還撃既狼狽相 (柒左又唔認):</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n自從本癲狗拆穿條肥閪得果158cm高同168磅重仲有大量on9自爆之後, 肥絲無力還擊, 只能以&quot;真心左&quot;, &quot;假膠&quot;等來反擊來掩飾自己既&quot;糗&quot;<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/6svpph81j/Excuse.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2F6svpph81j%2FExcuse.jpg&h=8bbd2f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 肥絲同佢班狗契仔既基本有以下既特質, 所以極度討厭本癲狗用以下詞彙形容佢地, 因為崩口狗忌崩口兜嘛<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 喜歡自己老母俾人屌<br />\n<br />\n- 老母是性工作者<br />\n<br />\n- 本身係狗 / 食屎狗 / 喜歡被撚<br />\n<br />\n- 小學雞<br />\n<br />\n- 容易被撚到嬲嬲豬/發嬲/發火<br />\n<br />\n- 肥西/肥閪<br />\n<br />\n- 基友/基佬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結: 其實肥絲都只不過係條人格唔健全既傻閪姐, 大家高抬貴手, 唔好玩到佢咁盡<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79e4bbd8d528ae3d699ca199a822b790d4dbdef2","tid":422362,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"話說肥鳩大隻條傻閪好自豪咁話自己捉錯字既on9回覆正評如潮，並沾沾自喜如下圖:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/6bnk6mu61/Screenshot_2017-09-20-14-43-16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2F6bnk6mu61%2FScreenshot_2017-09-20-14-43-16.png&h=367a62ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咦，睇過。。。條傻係唔係睇錯野，負評當左正評呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/gmzwzalvd/Screenshot_2017-09-20-14-33-46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fgmzwzalvd%2FScreenshot_2017-09-20-14-33-46.png&h=00e1d4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/oh53yfj21/Screenshot_2017-09-20-14-33-38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Foh53yfj21%2FScreenshot_2017-09-20-14-33-38.png&h=30bd48d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而屌鳩你條傻鳩既巴打大把人支持，佢既回覆先係正評娛潮wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/yfq2kwshl/Screenshot_2017-09-20-14-33-57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fyfq2kwshl%2FScreenshot_2017-09-20-14-33-57.png&h=86a8acab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等睇條傻鳩入黎發火兼賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6030613108ab960895150708da978a4f69393db5","tid":422362,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/wx6ks9uq1/1505721362017.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fwx6ks9uq1%2F1505721362017.png&h=31f16109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係&ldquo;嘅&rdquo;，唔係&ldquo;既&rdquo;呀on9仔</span></span><br />\n<